ngusamy]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Sarkar (2018 film)|Sarkar]]'' || Nila || [[AR Murugadoss]] || ||\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Manmadhudu 2]]'' || Suma || [[Rahul Ravindran]] || rowspan='2'|Telugu || Cameo appearance ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\"|2020 ||  scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"|  ''[[Miss India (film)|Miss India]]'' {{dagger}} || {{TBA}} || Narendra Nath  ||  post production ||<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thenewsminute.com/article/watch-keerthy-suresh-all-style-miss-india-teaser-107861%3famp|title=Watch: Keerthy Suresh is all style in 'Miss India' teaser|date=26 August 2019|website=The News Minute|archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|access-date=2019-08-31}}</ref>\n|- \n|scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"|  ''[[Marakkar: Arabikadalinte Simham]]'' {{dagger}} || Aarcha || [[Priyadarshan]] || Malayalam ||  post production || \n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"|  ''Penguin'' {{dagger}} || {{TBA}} || Eshwar || Tamil || post production ||<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/south/penguin-shoot-wrap-keerthy-suresh-gets-emotional-she-talks-about-sweet-and-memorable-journey-483494|title= Penguin shoot wrap up: Keerthy Suresh gets emotional as she talks about the sweet and memorable journey|date=3 November 2019|website=Pinkvilla| archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|access-date=2019-11-04}}</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"|''[[Good Luck Sakhi]] '' {{dagger}} || Sakhi || [[Nagesh Kukunoor]] || rowspan=\"2\"|Telugu||Filming ||<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/amp/movies/regional-cinema/story/keerthy-suresh-plays-a-sharpshooter-in-nagesh-kukunoor-s-good-luck-sakhi-1614134-2019-10-30|title=Keerthy Suresh plays a sharpshooter in Nagesh Kukunoor's 'Good Luck Sakhi'|date=30 October 2019|website=India Today| archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|access-date=2019-11-10}}</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"| ''Rang De'' {{dagger}} || Anu || Venky Atluri || Filming ||<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://jfwonline.com/article/rang-de-keerthy-suresh-nithiin-kick-start-their-shoot-with-a-pooja/|title=Rang De: Keerthy Suresh, Nithiin kick-starts their shoot with a Pooja !|date=8 October 2019|website=JFW online| archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|access-date=2019-11-09}}</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"| ''[[Annaatthe]]'' {{dagger}} || {{TBA}} || [[Siva (director)|Siva]]|| Tamil || Filming ||<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://m.timesofindia.com/entertainment/tamil/movies/news/rajinikanths-starts-shooting-for-thalaivar-168-in-hyderabad-today/amp_articleshow/72865881.cms|title=Rajinikanth's starts shooting for 'Thalaivar 168' in Hyderabad today|date=18 December 2019|website=[[Times of India]]| archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|access-date=2019-12-24}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n== Discography ==\nKeerthy has sung the following songs for her films:\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:10%;\"| Year\n! style=\"width:25%;\"| Film\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Song\n! style=\"width:10%;\"| Notes\n! Ref\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Saamy Square]]''\n| \"Pudhu Metro Rail\" \n| Duet with [[Vikram (actor)|Vikram]]\n| <ref>{{cite news |author=Anupama Subramanian |url=https://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/kollywood/280718/keerthy-suresh-sings-for-saamy-square.html|title=Keerthy Suresh sings for Saamy Square|website=Deccan Chronicle| accessdate=28 July 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Television==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! Year\n! Serial\n!Channel\n! Language\n! Notes\n!Ref\n|-\n|2004||''Santhana Gopalam''||[[Surya TV]]||Malayalam ||Child artist||<ref>[http://www.mangalam.com/mangalam-varika/84386 \u0d1e\u0d3e\u0d28\u0d4d\u200d \u0d15\u0d40\u0d30\u0d4d\u200d\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d24\u0d3f; \u0d2e\u0d47\u0d28\u0d15\u0d2f\u0d41\u0d1f\u0d46 \u0d2e\u0d15\u0d33\u0d4d\u200d]. mangalam.com (16 August 2013). Retrieved on 26 January 2014.</ref>\n|-\n|2005||''Krishna Kripa Sagaram''||[[Amrita TV]]||Malayalam ||Child artist ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/photo-features/keerthy-suresh-interesting-facts-about-the-mahanati-actress/as-a-child-artist/photostory/64093231.cms|title=As a child artist \u2013 Keerthy Suresh: Interesting facts about the 'Mahanati' actress \u2013 The Times of India|website=The Times of India|accessdate=24 August 2018}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{{refimprove|section|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox actor awards \n| name = Keerthy Suresh\n| image = \n| image_size = \n| alt = \n| caption =\n| wins = 11\n| nominations = 6\n}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Film\n! Result\n! {{Tooltip|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2014 \n| [[3rd South Indian International Movie Awards|South Indian International Movie Awards]] \n| Best Debutant Actress - Malayalam \n| ''Geethaanjali'' \n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| [[Asianet Film Awards]] \n| Best New Face of the year \n| ''Geethaanjali'' \n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| 2015 \n| [[Edison Awards (India)|Edison Awards]] \n| Best Female Rising Star \n| ''[[Idhu Enna Maayam]]'' \n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| 2016 \n| [[5th South Indian International Movie Awards|South Indian International Movie Awards]] \n| Best Debutant Actress - Tamil \n| ''Idhu Enna Maayam'' \n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"|2017 \n| [[Filmfare Awards South]] \n| [[64th Filmfare Awards South| Best Actress]] \n| rowspan=\"4\"|''[[Nenu Sailaja]]'' \n| {{nom}}\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/regional-cinema/story/64th-filmfare-awards-south-2017-full-nominations-list-983224-2017-06-17|title=64th Filmfare Awards South 2017: Here is the full nominations' list.|website=India Today|date=2017-06-17|access-date=2019-11-26}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[6th South Indian International Movie Awards|South Indian International Movie Awards]] \n| Best Debut Actress \u2013 Telugu\n| {{nom}}\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Zee Cinema]] Awards \n| Best Debutant Actress  \n| 